{"tid":545030,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"海上自衛隊最高機密：最強食譜","createTime":"2018-01-30T06:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T07:01:20.000Z","uid":66607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"650bd10122c222ee1c0d3ddb61e2d171dc164c9a","tid":545030,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T06:21:01.000Z","msg":"據說，在海陸空三個自衛隊裡，海上自衛隊的料理最好吃。他們有一個專門學習烹調的學校（第四術科學校），對食的要求很高。不加入自衛隊的話，就沒有機會吃到那些傳說中的料理。雖然沒有機會吃海上自衛隊親自烹調的料理，但現在有機會參考他們的食譜，煮給自己吃！ <br />\n<br />\n1月25日KADOKAWA出版社發售了《海上自衛隊 最強レシピ集 艦めし》（1,242円）。這本食譜有齊海上自衛隊各艦艇的珍藏料理煮法，數量高達五十種。例如有舊海軍的傳統料理咖哩飯，書本採用潛水艦雲龍號的無麩質咖哩，以及救難母艦千代田的千代田特製海鮮咖哩。還有特務艇橋立的巧克力蛋糕和其他甜品也一定要試製！<br />\n<br />\n另外，各艦隊活用當地新鮮食材，不只是和式料理，還有西式和中式料理。據作者所說，不同區域的自衛隊會在演習或者親善訪問時，與其他區域的隊員交換食譜。隊員指，即使沒有使用當地新鮮食材，也能還原料理應有的味道。若然真的不想親身下廚，又想吃到海上自衛隊的料理，可以找一些前自衛隊隊員開的餐廳吧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=6886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D6886&d=Ttds0xcXRO%2BjCWok1iePRdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=880cf299\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=6886</a>"},{"pid":"a1c4812a1a4eafa4922d17d83319dbbc0b8e2b05","tid":545030,"uid":134226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T06:23:59.000Z","msg":"星期五海軍咖喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d78e510011a29aa5b0b4b1be7aef39b450d9cb","tid":545030,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T06:49:38.000Z","msg":"香港有無餐廳有整？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746e7257f297b1de01b25f268d314c855eef953a","tid":545030,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"支那食泥水公仔麵啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbeaf39cea47c9da81908ab62a3d1d7043df3f0","tid":545030,"uid":37524,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://otakei.otakuma.net/wp/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/d21ff5329baaee77b3562e90ba20d548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fotakei.otakuma.net%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fd21ff5329baaee77b3562e90ba20d548.jpg&h=1cc10829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://otakei.otakuma.net/wp/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/26f7a18724c9634c9be82c72ab6b3acb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fotakei.otakuma.net%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F26f7a18724c9634c9be82c72ab6b3acb.jpg&h=a76baead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}